<L>__{interior bonaventure hotel shoeshine stand day 1:02pm}
<A>__{gene walks over, climbs into a chair.}
<C>__{huey}
<P>__{(still not looking up)}
<D>__{take ten, take a break, take a seat, take a load off. put the world in perspective.}
