<C>__{huey}
<D>__{so, are you a visitor or are you lucky enough to...}
<A>__{...and freezes, staring at the familiar pair of shoes.}
<C>__{huey}
<P>__{(as he looks up)}
<D>__{you got a complaint?}
<A>__{gene looks down at him.}
