<D>__{please. something is going to happen...}
<C>__{huey}
<D>__{what? the end of the world? man, don't give me your mad rap. i'm not a bartender. i don't want to hear it. i raise a family doing this bullshit. do me a favor. get your crazy white ass out of my chair.}
<C>__{gene}
<D>__{please...}
<C>__{huey}
<D>__{hey, a big tip doesn't give you the right to crap in my ear. you want change? you got it, brother. what was that you gave me, a twenty?}
